    "detail": "This was our first time to Da Nang, the hotel had great amenities, all a hotel has to offer including complimentary breakfast, a bottle water for each guest per day, gym, upstairs bar with an amazing view and an incredibly insane view from their infinity pool. The staff there was very friendly and always helpful in everything we needed. I was provided an later checkout and with a thank you gift at checkout. Iwould love to come stay here again on my next visit to Da Nang and highly recommend this hotel for anyone that stays in Da Nang.",
