  {
    "hotel_id": "6522912",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/everland-hotel_2/hotel/da-nang-vn.html",
    "name": "Everland Hotel",
    "detail": "This is a newly built high rise hotel in Da Nang, opened in early 2019. The staff is learning the ropes but the facility is first rate. There is only one restaurant in the immediate area surrounded by construction sites. Da Nang is booming, especially the area east of the river, but we found that area to be more pedestrian friendly than the older section across the river. The hotel is halfway between the endless beach and the river with several options for eating nearby. It's ideal for those who like to explore on foot. In spite of all the construction going on, our room was very quiet. Breakfast is excellent. Cable TV has over a dozen English channels. The rooftop pool has nice warm water. ",
